ience that captures booking fulfilment and expense  egencias first fully integrated expense management partner will be its affiliate traveldoo with other expense providers to follow   for more information on the egencia expense management suite please visit httpinfoegenciacomnaqproductexpensesuitehtml and stop by our stand at the business travel show in london february    about egencia egencia makes business travel better by making it more connected and complete egencia puts travelers at the heart of business travel continuously supporting them with solutions that are more engaging and effective driven by consumer insights and technology investments from parent company expedia inc egencia connects everything travelers need – content technology service and reporting – in one place egencia provides services in more than  countries to connect with egencia visit wwwegenciacom or egencia follow along on our blog at httpswwwegenciacompublicusresources   egencia llc  all rights reserved  egencia and the egencia logo are either registered trademarks or trademarks of expedia inc in the us andor other countries  all other trademarks are the property of their respective owners  cst   cst   to view the original version on pr newswire visithttpwwwprnewswirecomnewsreleasesegenciatolaunchnewexpenseproductsuitehtml source egencia related links httpwwwegenciacompublicusresources feb    et preview egencia and sabre make  the year of the business traveler jan    et preview egencia awards top  preferred corporate hotels for  my news release contains wide tables view fullscreen also from this source jul    et egencia expense on nyt saatavilla jul    et egencia expense is open for business explore more news releases in similar topics computer electronics travel industry new products  services you just read egencia to launch new expense product suite news provided by egencia feb    et share this article looking to send a news release with pr newswire take advantage of the worlds leading d